  <section id="embeds" class="flow">
    <h2>Embeds</h2>
    <p>A number of components are provided for embedding external content. Some of these are part of this site, while others are imported from <a href="https://astro-embed.netlify.app/">astro-embed</a>.</p>

    <h3 id="embed-lcvid">LCVid</h3>
    <p>
      The LCVid component renders self-hosted videos from my video platform. Metadata (title, description, duration, transcript) is fetched
      at build time from the video's JSON and clicking the video plays it using a <a href="https://vidstack.io/">Vidstack</a> player.
    </p>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Prop</th>
          <th>Type</th>
          <th>Default</th>
          <th>Description</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><code>src</code></td>
          <td><code>string</code></td>
          <td><em>required</em></td>
          <td>Full URL, absolute path, or bare slug on v.danny.is.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><code>title</code> / <code>description</code></td>
          <td><code>string</code></td>
          <td>—</td>
          <td>Override the copy fetched from the video's JSON.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td
            ><code>showTitle</code> / <code>showDescription</code> / <code>showMeta</code> / <code
              >showOpenLink</code
            ></td
          >
          <td><code>boolean</code></td>
          <td><code>true</code></td>
          <td>Toggle each piece of chrome around the player.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><code>showTranscript</code></td>
          <td><code>boolean</code></td>
          <td><code>false</code></td>
          <td>Reveal a collapsible transcript (when one exists in the JSON).</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h4>Default — full chrome</h4>
    <Code lang="mdx" code={'<LCVid src="lcdemo-part-2" />'} />
    <ResizableContainer>
      <LCVid src="lcdemo-part-2" />
    </ResizableContainer>

    <h4>With transcript</h4>
    <Code lang="mdx" code={'<LCVid src="lcdemo-part-2" showTranscript />'} />
    <ResizableContainer>
      <LCVid src="lcdemo-part-2" showTranscript />
    </ResizableContainer>

