    <h3 id="embed-auto">Embed (auto-dispatch)</h3>
    <p>
      The <code>&lt;Embed&gt;</code> component regex-matches a URL and renders the most appropriate
      component, so in prose you can paste almost any link and get a sensible embed. It dispatches YouTube,
      Vimeo, Tweet, Loom, v.danny.is (LCVid), GitHub Gist, Bluesky and Mastodon URLs to the components
      above — and falls back to a <code>&lt;BookmarkCard&gt;</code> for anything it doesn't recognise.
    </p>
    <p>
      <em
        >BaselineStatus has no URL to match against, so it isn't auto-dispatched — use the named
        component above.</em
      >
    </p>
    <Code
      lang="mdx"
      code={`<Embed url="https://youtu.be/xtTy5nKay_Y" />
<Embed url="https://v.danny.is/lcdemo-part-2" />
<Embed url="https://example.com" /> {/* no match → BookmarkCard */}`}
    />
    <p>An unrecognised URL falls back to a BookmarkCard:</p>
    <ResizableContainer>
      <Embed url="https://example.com" />
    </ResizableContainer>
